txt.en: North, beyond Umbar city, where the hills roll into the shore, sea-hawks soar above the land. They build nests in the crags and trees. They lay eggs prized by the chefs of Umbar. Collect the eggs and return to Luthana at the expedition camp.

North, beyond Umbar city, where the hills roll into the shore, sea-hawks soar above the land. They build nests in the crags and trees. They lay eggs prized by the chefs of Umbar. Collect the eggs and return to Luthana at the expedition camp.
'You will find eggs in sea-hawk nests north along the shore and the hills. Collect thirteen eggs and return them to me here at the encampment.'
'You will find eggs in sea-hawk nests north along the shore and the hills. Collect fourteen eggs and return them to me here at the encampment.'
Your efforts to collect sea-hawk eggs proved fruitful. All you need do now is return your precious cargo to Luthana at the hunter's expedition in the south-eastern portion of the Cape of Umbar.
Deliver the eggs to Luthana at the hunter's expedition

'Thank you for collecting these. I will deliver the eggs to the cooks' guild. The leadership will distribute them to their chefs. Those who pay will enjoy them in breakfast feasts throughout the city.'

Head north to where the hills meet the shore, and search the nests of the sea-hawks for unfertilized eggs. Collect fourteen eggs from the nests and return them to Luthana at the expedition encampment in the eastern part of the Cape of Umbar.

'Epicureans in the city desire sea-hawk eggs for their unique flavour and size. The birds make their nests north beyond the city, where the hills roll into the shore. Go north and seek out the sea-hawk nests, collect fourteen eggs from their nests, and return them to me.'
Deliver the sea-hawk eggs to Luthana at the expedition camp

'Thank you for collecting these. I will deliver the eggs to the cooks' guild. The leadership will distribute them to their chefs. Those who pay will enjoy them in breakfast feasts throughout the city.'
